function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	-- Get NPCs (and a Gate and Ritual FX)
	idDonan = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_DonanTomb")[1]
	idLorath = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_LorathTomb")[1]
	idNeyrelle = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_NeyrelleTomb")[1]
	idGate = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_TombGate")[1]
	idRitualFX = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_RitualFX")[1]
	
	-- Get locations
	idDonanLoc = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_DonanTombLoc")[1]
	idLorathLoc = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_LorathTombLoc")[1]
	idLorathLoc2 = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_LorathTombLoc2")[1]
	idLorathLoc3 = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_LorathTombLoc3")[1]
	idNeyrelleLoc = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_NeyrelleTombLoc")[1]
	idNeyrelleHelpLoc = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_NeyrelleTombHelpLoc")[1]
	idLorathRunLoc = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_LorathRunLoc")[1]
	idTaissa = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "Taissa")[1]
	
	-- Play Taissa calloutg
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_TAISSACALLOUT, idTaissa)
	
	-- Donan ritual ends
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idRitualFX, "fxKit_harmless_burstCylindrical_horadric")
	Hydra.ActorSetScriptedLookOverride(idRitualFX, "IGC Soulstone Mephisto Blue - On")
	Hydra.EventSend("RandomizedBanterEnd", idDonan)
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(CONV_RITUALBANTER)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idDonan, "fxKit_harmless_persistentRope_horadric")
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idLorath, "fxKit_harmless_persistentRope_horadric")
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idNeyrelle, "fxKit_harmless_persistentRope_horadric")
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idDonan, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_2hand_horadric")
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idLorath, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_2hand_horadric")
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idNeyrelle, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_1hand_horadric")
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPhaseJump(idDonan)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPhaseJump(idLorath)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPhaseJump(idNeyrelle)
	Hydra.QActorSetIdleAnim(idLorath, "AnimKey_Neutral")
	Hydra.QActorSetIdleAnim(idNeyrelle, "AnimKey_Neutral")
	Hydra.Wait(3)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(idRitualFX)
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONV_RITUALEND, idDonan)
	
	Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(idDonan, "AnimKey_Ground_Sit_Headinhands", 0)
	
	Hydra.QActorWait(idNeyrelle, 3)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNeyrelle, idNeyrelleHelpLoc, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceActor(idNeyrelle, idDonan)
	Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(idNeyrelle, "AnimKey_Use_Crouch", 0)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idLorath, CONV_RITUALEND)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLorath, idLorathRunLoc, "NPC_Run", true)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idLorath, 1)

	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, sWorldName)

	-- one is unique spawned from the graph, the other is in the gamelayer of the grave POI
	local tRevealHelpers = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("CSD_Hawe_Wetland_ZakFortCrypts_SecretDoor")
	for iter, idRevealer in pairs(tRevealHelpers) do
	
		Hydra.ActorSceneRevealSecretMap(idRevealer)
		
	end
	
	-- Get NPCs, a Gate, a fog wall ritual FX
	idDonan = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_DonanTomb")[1]
	idLorath = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_LorathTomb")[1]
	idNeyrelle = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_NeyrelleTomb")[1]
	idGate = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_TombGate")[1]
	idRitualFX = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_RitualFX")[1]
	idFogWall = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("CSD_ZakFortCrypts_BossRoom_FogWallExitBlocker")[1]

	
	-- Get locations
	idDonanLoc = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_DonanTombLoc")[1]
	idLorathLoc = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_LorathTombLoc")[1]
	idLorathLoc2 = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_LorathTombLoc2")[1]
	idLorathLoc3 = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_LorathTombLoc3")[1]
	idNeyrelleLoc = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_NeyrelleTombLoc")[1]
	idNeyrelleHelpLoc = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_NeyrelleTombHelpLoc")[1]
	idLorathRunLoc = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_LorathRunLoc")[1]
	
	-- Move actors to the right locations, set their idles
	Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(idDonan, idDonanLoc)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idDonan)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idDonan, idDonanLoc)
	Hydra.QActorWait(idDonan, 0.1)
	Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(idDonan, "AnimKey_Chant_Ritual_EyeLevel", 0)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idDonan, idRitualFX, "fxKit_harmless_persistentRope_horadric", true, "HP_Portrait", "HP_Mouth")
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idDonan, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_2hand_horadric", true)
	
	Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(idLorath, idLorathLoc)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idLorath)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idLorath, idLorathLoc)
	Hydra.QActorWait(idLorath, 0.1)
	Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(idLorath, "AnimKey_Chant_Ritual_Table", 0)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idLorath, idRitualFX, "fxKit_harmless_persistentRope_horadric", true, "HP_Portrait", "HP_Mouth")
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idLorath, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_2hand_horadric", true)
	
	Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(idNeyrelle, idNeyrelleLoc)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idNeyrelle)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idNeyrelle, idNeyrelleLoc)
	Hydra.QActorWait(idNeyrelle, 0.1)
	Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(idNeyrelle, "AnimKey_Chant_Ritual_Sky", 0)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idNeyrelle, idRitualFX, "fxKit_harmless_persistentRope_horadric", true, "HP_Portrait", "HP_Mouth")
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idNeyrelle, "fxKit_harmless_persistentCast_1hand_horadric", true)

	Hydra.ActorEnable(idRitualFX)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(idGate)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idFogWall)
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	idElias = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "ELIAS")[1]
	
	
	local followerTaissa = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Taissa_Witch_Follower")
	local followerLorath = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lorath_Follower")
	idTaissa = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_TaissaSwampElias")[1]
	idLorath = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Hawe_Finale_LorathSwampElias")[1]
	
	--Take control of followerLorath and send him to idLorath
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerLorath) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerLorath)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerLorath, idLorath, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerLorath, idLorath)
	end
	
	--Take control of followerTaissa and send her to idTaissa
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerTaissa) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(followerTaissa)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(followerTaissa, idTaissa, "NPC_Run", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(followerTaissa, idTaissa)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerLorath) then
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerLorath)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(followerLorath, 0)
	end
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(followerTaissa) then
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(followerTaissa)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(followerTaissa, 0)
	end
	
end
